24:["$","p",null,{"className":"text-gray-500 text-xs md:text-sm leading-relaxed line-clamp-2 mb-3","children":"The European Union's Cyber Resilience Act (CRA) has entered its first enforcement phase, requiring all connected device manufacturers selling in the EU to demonstrate baseline cybersecurity properties. Non-compliant products face market withdrawal orders and fines up to €15 million or 2.5% of global turnover."}]
